== 开发和制作 ==
2008年11月11日[[AMC_(电视频道)|AMC频道]]宣布开发一部名为《Rectify》的电视剧<ref>[http://www.amcnetworks.com/release_release_press.jsp?nodeid=5929 AMC Announces Rectify as New Series in Development]{{dead link|date=2018年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2008/11/11/amc-announces-rectify-as-new-series-in-development--29491/20081111amc01/ |title=AMC Announces Rectify as New Series in Development |access-date=2013-04-30 |archive-date=2021-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325041327/https://www.google-analytics.com/ga.js |dead-url=no }}</ref>，三年后和AMC属于同一公司的日舞频道于2011年10月31日宣布预定该剧并表示第一季将有6集<ref>[http://www.amcnetworks.com/release_release_press.jsp?nodeid=6433 Sundance Channel Greenlights Original Scripted Series Rectify]{{dead link|date=2018年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2011/10/31/sundance-channel-greenlights-original-scripted-series-rectify-718115/20111031sundance01/ |title=Sundance Channel Greenlights Original Scripted Series "Rectify" |access-date=2013-04-30 |archive-date=2021-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325041327/https://www.google-analytics.com/ga.js |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年5月11日日舞频道宣布的2012至2013季度安排中显示本剧将于2013年播出<ref>[http://www.amcnetworks.com/release_release_press.jsp?nodeid=6525 Sundance Channel Unveils Non-Fiction Development Slate for 2012/2013 Season] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120609061239/http://www.amcnetworks.com/release_release_press.jsp?nodeid=6525 |date=2012-06-09 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2012/05/11/sundance-channel-unveils-non-fiction-development-slate-for-2012-2013-season-982105/20120511sundance01/ Sundance Channel Unveils Non-Fiction Development Slate for 2012/2013 Season]</ref>，6月份的新闻稿再次确认于2013年播出<ref>[http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2012/06/29/sundance-channels-programming-overview-for-the-remainder-of-2012-and-the-beginning-of-2013-215111/20120629sundance01/ Sundance Channel's Programming Overview for the Remainder of 2012 and the Beginning of 2013]</ref>。2012年12月12日日舞频道宣布本节目将于2013年4月22日起10:00PM ET/PT播出<ref>[http://www.amcnetworks.com/release_release_press.jsp?nodeid=6608 Sundance Channel Announces 'RECTIFY,' Networks's First Wholly Owned Original Scripted Series To Debut April 22, 2013 at 10:00PM ET/PT] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130727225226/http://www.amcnetworks.com/release_release_press.jsp?nodeid=6608 |date=2013年7月27日 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2012/12/12/sundance-channel-announces-rectify-networks-first-wholly-owned-original-scripted-series-to-debut-april-22-2013-at-1000pm-et-pt-571310/20121212sundance01/ Sundance Channel Announces "Rectify," Network's First Wholly Owned Original Scripted Series To Debut April 22, 2013 at 10:00PM ET/PT]</ref>，随后电视台决定将在首播日连续播放两集<ref>[http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2013/04/08/sundance-channel-partners-with-art-house-convergence-and-sundance-cinemas-to-sneak-peek-the-networks-upcoming-drama-series-rectify-at-more-than-a-dozen-theaters-nationwide-on-tuesday-april-16th-724212/20130408sundance01/ Sundance Channel Partners with Art House Convergence and Sundance Cinemas to Sneak Peek the Network's Upcoming Drama Series "Rectify" at More Than a Dozen Theaters Nationwide on Tuesday, April 16th]</ref>。

=== 选角 ===
2012年4月25日日舞频道宣布阿比盖尔·斯宾塞、克莱恩·克劳福德、雅德蕾德·克莱门斯、乔纳·坍和J·史密斯-卡梅伦将出演本剧<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/04/quintet-of-actors-cast-in-sundance-channels-drama-series-rectify/ |title=Quintet Of Actors Cast In Sundance Channel’s Drama Series ‘Rectify’ |accessdate=2013-04-29 |archive-date=2013-05-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130504095507/http://www.deadline.com/2012/04/quintet-of-actors-cast-in-sundance-channels-drama-series-rectify/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年5月31日确定将由亚丁·杨担任本剧主角丹尼尔·霍顿<ref>[http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2012/05/31/sundance-channel-casts-aden-young-as-lead-in-original-scripted-series-rectify-893203/20120531sundance01/ Sundance Channel Casts Aden Young as Lead in Original Scripted Series "Rectify"]</ref>。

2012年6月13日确认卢克·科比加盟本片饰演乔恩·斯特恩<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://variety.com/2012/tv/news/luke-kirby-cast-in-sundance-s-rectify-1118055456/ |title=Thesp to play lawyer in cabler's first original scripted skein |accessdate=2013-04-30 |archive-date=2013-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130920200039/http://variety.com/2012/tv/news/luke-kirby-cast-in-sundance-s-rectify-1118055456/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

